<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Look Infinito | Peluquería y Estética en Barcelona</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Look Infinito Peluquería y Estética en Sant Gervasi, Barcelona. Coloración, mechas, corte, peinado, keratina y estética. Reserva por teléfono o WhatsApp." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#141210" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #fffaf7;
      --bg-soft: #fff5ef;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      --card-strong: #ffffff;
      --text: #231f1b;
      --muted: #6f665f;
      --line: rgba(72, 59, 50, 0.12);
      --rose: #d84c83;
      --rose-dark: #b8376a;
      --rose-soft: #fde7ef;
      --amber-soft: #fff4d8;
      --dark: #141210;
      --dark-2: #2b2521;
      --shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(27, 20, 16, 0.08);
      --shadow-lg: 0 24px 60px rgba(27, 20, 16, 0.14);
      --radius: 26px;
      --radius-sm: 18px;
      --container: 1200px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(244,114,182,.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(251,191,36,.16), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(to bottom, #fffaf7, #fff5ef 28%, #fffaf7 100%);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section { padding: 88px 0; }
    .section-soft { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff5ef 0%, #fffaf7 100%); }
    .section-bordered {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(184, 55, 106, .88);
    }

    .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    header {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 24px 0;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: .96rem;
      transition: transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, background-color .2s ease, border-color .2s ease, color .2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: #211d1a; }

    .btn-outline {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      border-color: rgba(48, 36, 29, .18);
      color: var(--text);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 8px 0 96px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 11px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,76,131,.16);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.82);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      color: #4d433d;
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose), #f59ac0);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(216,76,131,.11);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 22px 0 0;
      max-width: 780px;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 4.8rem);
      line-height: .98;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }

    .hero p.hero-copy {
      margin: 22px 0 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .highlights {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .mini-card, .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .mini-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #574d47;
      min-height: 72px;
    }

    .check {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--rose-soft);
      color: var(--rose-dark);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .visual-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .hero-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.84);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.7);
    }

    .hero-card-main {
      grid-column: span 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card-main .media {
      min-height: 320px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-card-main img, .gallery-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .media::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(20,18,16,.18), transparent 54%);
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .kicker {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(184, 55, 106, .88);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .22em;
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    .card h3, .hero-card h3 {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      font-size: 1.72rem;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .card p, .hero-card p {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-list {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: .96rem;
      color: #514741;
    }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .icon-bullet {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--rose-soft);
      color: var(--rose-dark);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2px;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .gallery-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.75);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .gallery-card .image-wrap {
      height: 224px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .placeholder {
      height: 224px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde7ef, #f6efe7, #fff4d8);
    }

    .placeholder .big {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .services-grid,
    .testimonials-grid,
    .faq-grid,
    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); margin-top: 38px; }
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); margin-top: 38px; }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); margin-top: 28px; }

    .service-card,
    .testimonial-card,
    .faq-card,
    .contact-panel,
    .cta-panel,
    .feature-item {
      background: var(--card-strong);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .service-card,
    .testimonial-card,
    .faq-card,
    .feature-item {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .service-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--rose-soft);
      color: var(--rose-dark);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .service-card h3,
    .faq-card h3,
    .feature-item h4,
    .testimonial-card .name {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      background: #fffaf7;
    }

    .stars {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      color: #dba834;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .testimonial-card blockquote {
      margin: 0;
      color: #574d47;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .testimonial-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .testimonial-role {
      font-size: .77rem;
      color: #82766f;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--rose-soft);
      color: var(--rose-dark);
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr .95fr;
      gap: 46px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .chev {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--rose-soft);
      color: var(--rose-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .contact-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark) 0%, #231d1a 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 34px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .contact-panel p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.74);
    }

    .contact-links {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .contact-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      transition: background-color .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .contact-link .left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-link .label {
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.68);
    }

    .contact-link .value {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .faq-card p { margin-top: 12px; }

    .cta-panel {
      overflow: hidden;
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #141210, #2b2521, #5a3143);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 42px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .cta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
      gap: 34px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-panel p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 28px 0 96px;
      color: #6f665f;
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

    .footer-title {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2f2925;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: #221d1a; }

    .mobile-bar {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 16px;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 0 14px;
      display: none;
    }

    .mobile-bar-inner {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .mobile-bar .btn { flex: 1; min-height: 50px; }
    .mobile-bar .btn-rose {
      background: var(--rose);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .mobile-bar .btn-rose:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); }

    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
    }

    .fade-up.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .two-col,
      .split,
      .cta-grid,
      .hero-card-main {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .highlights { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .hero-card-main { grid-column: auto; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .section { padding: 72px 0; }
      .nav { align-items: flex-start; }
      .actions { display: none; }
      .hero { padding-bottom: 74px; }
      .visual-grid,
      .services-grid,
      .testimonials-grid,
      .faq-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .highlights {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .footer-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding-bottom: 112px;
      }
      .mobile-bar { display: block; }
      .container { width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 24px)); }
      .contact-panel,
      .cta-panel,
      .service-card,
      .testimonial-card,
      .faq-card,
      .hero-card .card-content,
      .gallery-card .card-content {
        padding-left: 22px;
        padding-right: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "HairSalon",
      "name": "Look Infinito Peluquería y Estética",
      "image": [
        "https://cdn1.treatwell.net/images/view/v2.i8210124.w1080.h720.xCB6997BB/",
        "https://cdn1.treatwell.net/images/view/v2.i1644952.w1080.h720.x972F7369/"
      ],
      "telephone": "+34 938 48 86 94",
      "email": "yanirapaniaguard@hotmail.com",
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "streetAddress": "Pg. de St. Gervasi, 36",
        "postalCode": "08022",
        "addressLocality": "Barcelona",
        "addressRegion": "Barcelona",
        "addressCountry": "ES"
      },
      "areaServed": "Barcelona",
      "priceRange": "€€",
      "aggregateRating": {
        "@type": "AggregateRating",
        "ratingValue": "4.8",
        "reviewCount": "64"
      },
      "sameAs": [
        "https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Pg.+de+St.+Gervasi,+36,+08022+Barcelona"
      ],
      "makesOffer": [
        { "@type": "Offer", "itemOffered": { "@type": "Service", "name": "Coloración y mechas" } },
        { "@type": "Offer", "itemOffered": { "@type": "Service", "name": "Corte y peinado" } },
        { "@type": "Offer", "itemOffered": { "@type": "Service", "name": "Tratamiento capilar keratina" } },
        { "@type": "Offer", "itemOffered": { "@type": "Service", "name": "Manicura y pedicura" } }
      ]
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <div>
        <div class="brand-title">Look Infinito</div>
        <div class="brand-subtitle">Peluquería y Estética · Barcelona</div>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Pg.+de+St.+Gervasi,+36,+08022+Barcelona" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Cómo llegar</a>
        <a class="btn btn-dark" href="tel:+34938488694">Llamar ahora</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <div class="badge"><span class="dot"></span> 4,8/5 en Google · 64 reseñas</div>
        <h1>Belleza, color y cuidado capilar con estilo propio en Sant Gervasi.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">Una landing pensada para transmitir confianza desde el primer segundo: servicios claros, reseñas visibles, llamada a la acción inmediata y enfoque local para captar citas en Barcelona.</p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/34938488694?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20pedir%20cita%20en%20Look%20Infinito" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Reservar por WhatsApp</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Pg.+de+St.+Gervasi,+36,+08022+Barcelona" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Ver ubicación</a>
        </div>

        <div class="highlights">
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>4,8/5 en Google</span></div>
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>64 reseñas públicas</span></div>
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Ubicación en Sant Gervasi</span></div>
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Teléfono directo para citas</span></div>
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Especialistas en mechas, color y keratina</span></div>
          <div class="mini-card"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Atención cercana y personalizada</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="visual-grid fade-up">
        <article class="hero-card hero-card-main">
          <div class="media">
            <img src="https://cdn1.treatwell.net/images/view/v2.i8210124.w1080.h720.xCB6997BB/" alt="Look Infinito Peluquería y Estética" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="kicker">Look Infinito Peluquería y Estética</p>
            <h3>Un salón cercano, cuidado y orientado al resultado.</h3>
            <p>La propuesta combina peluquería y estética con foco en atención personalizada, coloración, mechas, corte, keratina y servicios complementarios de belleza.</p>
            <div class="contact-list">
              <div class="contact-item"><span class="icon-bullet">📍</span><span>Pg. de St. Gervasi, 36, 08022 Barcelona</span></div>
              <div class="contact-item"><span class="icon-bullet">☎</span><span>938 48 86 94</span></div>
              <div class="contact-item"><span class="icon-bullet">⏰</span><span>Consulta por teléfono o WhatsApp para confirmar disponibilidad y horario.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="gallery-card">
          <div class="image-wrap">
            <img src="https://cdn1.treatwell.net/images/view/v2.i1644952.w1080.h720.x972F7369/" alt="Look Infinito fachada" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Look Infinito</h3>
            <p>Fachada / referencia visual pública</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="gallery-card">
          <div class="placeholder">
            <div>
              <div class="big">Galería lista para crecer</div>
              <p>Sustituye este bloque por fotos reales de resultados, interior o equipo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Resultados y estilo</h3>
            <p>Bloque preparado para sustituir por fotos reales</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Servicios</p>
